<emphasis id="753A496BD28D3020AF2C4A36E01AE374" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="55">Pileipellis</emphasis>
a trichoderm with terminal cells (22-) 35-75 (-105) 
<normalizedToken id="7F626A305AD79D94AA656F92902FE507" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
