<normalizedToken id="2766D47A9E873FDD6001E71579FCAA1E" originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
, cylindrical to subclavate, hyaline in KOH, yellowish in 
<normalizedToken id="65529F501A150CA6EF90022DAA737C67" originalValue="Melzer’s">Melzer's</normalizedToken>
